name: RebelPopcorn
0:
”Alexa, open Rebel Popcorn”
”Tell me about Sea Salt Caramel”
”Alexa, ask Rebel Popcorn about upcoming flavors”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: rebel popcorn
des:
Get up-to-date information on Rebel Popcorn flavors. 

For information about a flavor, just say "tell me about the flavor" and the flavor name, such as Sea Salt Caramel or Broncos Fever.

For our location, say "location". For hours, say "hours".

To find out what flavors are coming out of the kitchen, just say "upcoming flavors", "current flavors", or "always available flavors".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
